description:
CapacityKey: Table containing metadata describing capacity keys for radio access network resources.

- dateTime: Timestamp of data record creation.
- Area_Name: Name of the geographical area (e.g., NR_Balikpapan).
- CellId: Unique identifier of the cell site.
- Id2: Redundant Cell ID.
- Id3:  (Likely an unused or placeholder ID).
- Id4:  Combined capacity key ID with versioning.
- vsDataType: Type of data (vsDataCapacityKey).
- vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format (EricssonSpecificAttributes).
- CapacityKey.licensedCapacityLimit: Licensed capacity limit (appears to be empty).
- CapacityKey.licensedCapacityLimitReached: Boolean indicating if the licensed capacity limit is reached.
- CapacityKey.shared: Indication of shared capacity (appears to be empty).
- CapacityKey.name: Name of the capacity key type (e.g., UlBasebandCapacity).
- CapacityKey.grantedCapacityLevel: Granted capacity level.
- CapacityKey.keyId: Base capacity key identifier.
- CapacityKey.expiration: Expiration date of the capacity key (appears to be empty).
- CapacityKey.state: Detailed state information of the capacity key.
- CapacityKey.validFrom: Start date of capacity key validity.
- CapacityKey.capacityKeyId: Capacity key ID (including version).
- CapacityKey.productType: Type of product related to the capacity (e.g., Baseband).
